\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the framework for the designation,
 governance,
 execution,
 and closure of IT projects within the Elko County Information Operations Department,
 governing the full project lifecycle from charter through post-mortem.
 This policy ensures that project work is formally authorized,
 documented,
 and governed in alignment with the Department's governance obligations and service commitments.
\end_layout

