\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
In external projects,
 the sponsoring department or entity provides direction on business objectives and outcomes.
 The Information Operations Department retains full authority over technical design,
 security compliance,
 architecture decisions,
 and all IT governance obligations established in this manual.
 External project sponsors hold no supervisory or directive authority over Information Operations Personnel or IT technical determinations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
